Chris Broussard and Rob Parker are in for Dan & the Danettes, and they’re telling you why the Nets winning the NBA title would be bad for the NBA, wondering if there’s another athlete as influential as Jackie Robinson, and LA Rams wide receiver Robert Woods joins the show!
